      "score": 0.04163221121088036,
      "text": "Martine Blanc\nMartine Blanc (born 16 September 1944 in Clermont-Ferrand, Puy-de-Dôme) is a French author and illustrator of ten books for children including \"The story of Timothy\", the \"Two Hoots\" series in collaboration with Helen Cresswell, and \"All about Jesus\".",
