      "title": "Glenda Goss",
      "score": 0.04147120296338721,
      "text": "Glenda Goss\nGlenda Goss is an American author and music historian whose special interests are music and culture, early modernism, critical editing, and European-American points of cultural contact. Her most notable work has revolved around the life and works of the Finnish composer, Jean Sibelius.",
      "score_breakdown": {
