      "title": "The Red Tree (Shaun Tan)",
      "score": 0.0980174540947289,
      "text": "The Red Tree (Shaun Tan)\nThe Red Tree (2001), written and illustrated by Shaun Tan, is a picture book that presents a fragmented journey through a dark world. The illustrations are surreal. The text is sparse and matches the dark illustrations.",
      "score_breakdown": {
        "dense": 0.05095160617638037,
        "graph": 0.057056951788164646,
